data.description: Location, Location, Location! Do not miss out on your chance to own an investment in this desirable midtown neighborhood of Tuxedo Park, just walking distance to Miracle Mile. Nestled on the highly desirable tree-lined Bedford Road, this lovely home has been beautifully updated and added to, retaining its original charm while adding the convenience of modern day amenities. The main house features apx. 1400sq ft, 3-bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, with the master suite on the main floor. The upstairs unit is approximately 400 sq ft and features an updated one-bed/one-bathroom, loft style unit with a separate entrance and new mini split. Another fully restored, 400sq ft, one-bedroom/one-bath home sits at the back of the property. The entire property is equipped with updated plumbing, electrical and HVAC. Also featured is a newer roof and newer windows throughout. Come take a look at this perfect investment property,  just a few minutes walk to the Miracle Mile, which offers endless options for great shopping and dining! This perfect home has all the historic midtown charm you could ask for!
